<p>
<note n="0079001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0079001">悕＝希【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0079002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0079002">〔世尊〕－【三】【宮】</note>
